{"tid":1702552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有校巴司機被搶劫","createTime":"2019-11-09T17:52:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T01:40:25.000Z","uid":50386,"like":88,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"0027627aa08fa07708fe020c87b7ba2748b5a6c1","tid":1702552,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:52:26.000Z","msg":"朋友頭先做校巴，<br />\n載左兩個黑口罩男人由添馬去井欄樹白石窩，<br />\n一到步兩條友即刻箍頸掩口想搶野<br />\n好彩朋友佢響長銨叫救命驚動附近村民出黎幫手<br />\n兩條友搶咗個冇貴重嘢嘅袋就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做校巴嘅記得盡量搵副駕唔好單獨揸<br />\n或者覺得唔對路就響旺區趕佢落車<br />\n同埋去偏僻地方要停大路唔好入村路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢啲case報案都冇用，黑狗不知幾想趕絕校巴<br />\n而家搭校巴嘅危險，揸校巴要防臥底又要防賊仲危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad5ef56a574c377fd4456e32503deb8a04214ee","tid":1702552,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:53:23.000Z","msg":"有無人覺得香港無希望好想死？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702505\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702505</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"338f1431dd02233bc8c242ed6f33ad2ecedf7d2b","tid":1702552,"uid":125542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:53:43.000Z","msg":"屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0a70d2a04e6c1fa388c94fbc21bb5d6c108b9d","tid":1702552,"uid":294,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:54:12.000Z","msg":"一路都覺得校巴好危險, 你點知上車唔係狗<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1de1b3c00d0f11fc7d30f893a3c0a0e85f4a92f","tid":1702552,"uid":146520,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T17:56:02.000Z","msg":"又一證明藍屍真係社會最低賤敗類<br />\n窮到姦淫擄掠咩都做齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59510644e5a55a869ed0caa5cc46c8f5a6b7c7de","tid":1702552,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"